利率，为何出现存款利率「调降潮」？国有四大行会降低存款利率吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "4 月以来，广东、湖北、陕西、河南等多个省份的中小银行纷纷发布公告，下调人民币存款挂牌利率，涉及活期存款、定期存款、大额存单等，不同期限调整幅度不同。 接受《经济参考报》采访的专家表示，去年以来，在市场利率总体有所下行的背景下，国有大型银行和部分股份制银行纷纷下调存款利率，此次调整可视为中小银行的「跟进」，是其为压低负债成本所作的市场化定价行为。专家提示，未来存款利率仍存在下行空间，广大居民可根据个人需求，衡量收益与风险的关系，进行多元化资产配置。中小银行存款利率集体「补降」 未来或进一步下行 _ 经济参考网 _ 新华社《经济参考报》官方网站"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-28d9c4536905ba01b9ff9e881cc34eb1_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "37 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/597096718"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIra23/6Wz4Md2EAMaCDk0OTY4OTM5IK6hjaIGMAE4+QFAE3IJNTk3MDk2NzE4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1682219040.609243", "card_id": "Q_63833021", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 446}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "郭靖在晚年有多强？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-64ec772974214394849f26c18f01c42b_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "35 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/63833021"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIra23/6Wz4Md2EAMaCDE3NzU5MDEzIO6Vv8wFMBQ4+BRAFHIINjM4MzMwMjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1682219040.6099622", "card_id": "Q_596276145", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 50}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在路上骑车时，被人当破风工具人怎么办?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我是怕他撞上来"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-95af98ab2bec8b9f370baf690d616b7e_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "32 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0,